title: Get to know Lahiki Minamishin!
description: Lahiki Minamishin is a 12-year-old ripper from the Big Island of Hawaii. He can usually be found surfing his local spot Banyans but sometimes branches out to surf some of Hawaii's neighboring islands and beyond. Check out this video of young Lahiki...
